# 1.3.2 repairTheStreet

## LÃ¶sung

```java
void repairTheStreet() {
    repeat (9) {
        maybeRepair();
        moveForward();
    }
    maybeRepair();
}

void maybeRepair() {
    if (rightIsClear()) {
        turnRight();
        moveForward();
        dropBeeper();
        turnAround();
        moveForward();
        turnRight();
    }
}
```
#### 1.3.2 repairTheStreet
void repairTheStreet()
{
    repeat (10)
    {
        if (rightIsClear())
        {
            repair();    
        }
        else if (frontIsClear())
        {
            moveForward();
        }
    }
}

void repair()
{
    turnRight();
    moveForward();
    turnAround();
    dropBeeper();
    moveForward();
    turnRight();
    if(frontIsClear())
    {
    moveForward();
    }
    
}
